content: Brilliant app forna large age range
I paid to get a good app. But the application doesn't play the songs. There's no volume or music played to the songs. Highly disappointed. I need my money back
Can you open this app on a computer?
Is there an option to play all the songs? I want to play it in the car while I'm driving and I don't want to keep pressing next.
Like Jolly Phonica in AMERICAN ENGLISH. Not worth a penny to me in BRITISH.
replyContent: You can switch to American English by tapping the 'information' button in the top left of the home screen. I hope this helps.
On the /ck/ song, there is a toggle on the top right hand side of the screen; it automatically plays the c song but you can change to k by tapping this button.

content: Love but one issue does not have an index,. Meaning to go through all to get to the one I want.
replyContent: Glad to hear you like the app. There is an index! Touch the home button then the Info (i) button. You will see all the songs listed within a scrollable view and you can touch one to go straight to that song :)

content: If this app can be added google chromecast feature that can be play on big TV screen, it will get 5 stars from me.
